This magic longbow is particularly heavy (about 9 pounds). Once per day, when loosing an arrow from this bow, you can cause that arrow to cast [[gravity well]] wherever it lands. After you use this ability, the bow's weight drops to 3 pounds until the ability recharges the next day.

